@DATABASE "Ball Breaker 2"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - B - Ball Breaker 2"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - B
                   ====================================

                              Ball Breaker 2
                              ==============


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35874,0)"}          35874,0
@{"Infinite Ammo " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(39883,0)"}          39883,0
@{"Lives = x     " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35734,255)"}          35734,x (x= 1-255)
@{"Ammo = x      " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(35728,255)"}          35728,x (x= 1-255)

                         Change x to whatever value you wish, using
                         the POKE option on the ZXAM GUI. Simply
                         click the button to get the maximum value
                         x can be (usually 255).


                         This is one of my POKEs (Well, the X lives & ammo
                         POKEs are mine. Someone else had already done the
                         Infinite POKEs before I realised it). Enjoy!

                         Rastan.
@endnode
